    "[5], Li et al. [30][31][32]35], Li and Tang [34], where methods have been designed to combine information from distinct modalities.",
    "This section uncovers some existing works related to our approach, examining them in terms of feature extraction and multimodal action recognition approaches.",
    "Feature extractionFeature extraction is a process for yielding critical information from raw instances, which in turn contributes to the learning process.",
    "Temporal Segment Network (TSN) is used as a feature extractor based on its temporal pooling of frame-level features, where it has been rigorously used as an efficient video feature extractor for different problems.",
    "Gate-Shift Module (GSM) can turn a 2D CNN into a highly efficient spatio-temporal feature extractor."
